<div class="shead rv"><div class="spec-lab"><span class="b">—</span> how we work</div><h2>Idea to market — <span class="it">fast</span></h2><p>Our process is built for speed: AI gets us to a real product in days, then we ship and iterate with real users.</p></div>
<div class="aiwrap">
<ul class="ailist rv">
<li><span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 3l2.2 5.5L20 10l-4.5 3.4L17 19l-5-3-5 3 1.5-5.6L4 10l5.8-1.5z"/></svg></span><div><h3>1 · Idea → AI mockup</h3><p>Your idea becomes a clickable mockup the same day, with AI.</p></div></li>
<li><span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8 7l-4 5 4 5M16 7l4 5-4 5"/></svg></span><div><h3>2 · Build &amp; test</h3><p>We deploy fast and put it in front of real users — early.</p></div></li>
<li><span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 11a8 8 0 10-2.3 6.3"/><path d="M20 4v6h-6"/></svg></span><div><h3>3 · Iterate</h3><p>Validate, refine and harden — quickly, with feedback.</p></div></li>
<li><span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8"/></svg></span><div><h3>4 · Launch to market</h3><p>We focus on shipping fast — then scale the product.</p></div></li>
</ul>
<div class="ailog rv"><div class="bar"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div><div class="ln"><span class="pr">$</span> qdn ai mockup --from-brief</div><div class="ln"><span class="mut">→ generated 8 screens</span> <span class="ok">✓</span></div><div class="ln"><span class="mut">→ clickable prototype ready</span> <span class="ok">✓</span></div><div class="ln"><span class="mut">→ deployed to preview</span> <span class="ok">✓</span></div><div class="ln"><span class="mut">→ shared for review · day 1</span> <span class="text-accent">!</span></div><div class="res">≈ <b>weeks faster</b> to market — human-finished.</div></div>
</div></div></section>

<!-- PRODUCTS -->
<section class="sec pt-0"><div class="wrap"><div class="shead rv"><div class="spec-lab"><span class="b">—</span> our products</div><h2>We build our own <span class="it">SaaS</span>, too</h2><p>The clearest proof we build premium products — software we designed, shipped and run ourselves.</p></div>
<div class="specs">
<div class="sp rv"><div class="top"><span class="id">QDN-001</span><span>live</span></div><div class="in"><div class="pn">QOne</div><div class="pt">Project · HR · Expense platform</div><ul><li>Project &amp; task tracking</li><li>Human resources</li><li>Expense tracking</li></ul></div></div>
<div class="sp rv"><div class="top"><span class="id">QDN-002</span><span>live</span></div><div class="in"><div class="pn">SAT AI</div><div class="pt">AI-native learning platform</div><ul><li>AI-generated questions</li><li>Adaptive paths</li><li>Practice tests</li></ul></div></div>
<div class="sp rv"><div class="top"><span class="id">QDN-003</span><span>live</span></div><div class="in"><div class="pn">PropManage</div><div class="pt">Property management</div><ul><li>Property &amp; tenants</li><li>Financial tracking</li><li>Maintenance flows</li></ul></div></div>
