<!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
<section class="sec pt-0"><div class="wrap"><div class="shead ctr rv"><div class="spec-lab justify-center"><span class="b">—</span> what clients say</div><h2>Trusted to <span class="it">deliver</span></h2></div><div class="tst">
<div class="tcard rv"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p class="q">"We saw a clickable mockup the next day, and the MVP shipped in five weeks. Incredibly fast — and it held up."</p><div class="who"><span class="av">AL</span><div><h3>Alex L.</h3><span>Founder · SaaS startup</span></div></div></div>
<div class="tcard rv"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p class="q">"They use AI the right way: speed where it helps, human judgment where it matters. We felt the difference."</p><div class="who"><span class="av">MN</span><div><h3>Minh N.</h3><span>Product Lead</span></div></div></div>
<div class="tcard rv"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p class="q">"Clear communication, premium result, and to market faster than anyone we talked to."</p><div class="who"><span class="av">RT</span><div><h3>Rachel T.</h3><span>Operations Director</span></div></div></div>
</div></div></section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="sec pt-0"><div class="wrap"><div class="shead ctr rv"><div class="spec-lab justify-center"><span class="b">—</span> faq</div><h2>Questions, <span class="it">answered</span></h2></div><div class="faq rv">
<details open><summary>How fast can we see something?<span class="pm"></span></summary><div class="ans">Usually a clickable AI mockup within a day of kickoff — so you can react to a real product, not a slide.</div></details>
<details><summary>How fast to launch?<span class="pm"></span></summary><div class="ans">Most MVPs reach the market in 2–6 weeks. We deploy early to test, then focus on shipping fast.</div></details>
<details><summary>How does AI fit in?<span class="pm"></span></summary><div class="ans">AI builds mockups and accelerates code, tests and docs. We finish by hand, to a premium standard.</div></details>
<details><summary>Do we own the code and IP?<span class="pm"></span></summary><div class="ans">Yes — you own all code, designs and IP. No lock-in.</div></details>
<details><summary>How do we start?<span class="pm"></span></summary><div class="ans">Book a consultation. We scope it, build a mockup fast, and go from there — usually within days.</div></details>
</div></div></section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="sec"><div class="wrap"><div class="cta rv"><div class="spec-lab"><span class="b">→</span> make your move</div><h2>Let's build your <span class="it">product</span>.</h2><p class="s">Tell us the idea. We'll get you a mockup fast — and a premium product to market, early.</p><div class="flex gap-3 justify-center flex-wrap"><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-paper">Start a project <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a><a href="#how" class="btn btn-ghost">See how we work</a></div></div></div></section>
